// transposition3 — silent sound objects rewrite
// Original: -gr.transposition3 (Harm Visser, 1997)
// _transpose = runtime → _script(CTn) via SUB1
RND
gram#1[1] S --> A /numtimes=5/
gram#1[2] A --> {E1, A#1 F#1} {Tr2 D}
gram#1[3] B --> {Tr2 A}
gram#1[4] C --> {Tr4 B}
gram#1[5] /numtimes-1/ D --> - {Tr6 C {1,B}} {1,C} _repeat(4)
------------
SUB1
gram#2[1] Tr2 --> _script(CT 0)
gram#2[2] Tr4 --> _script(CT 1)
gram#2[3] Tr6 --> _script(CT 2)
gram#2[4] D --> lambda
